Summary: Took photos of sunset while out to sea and captured two UFO'S
divs: Sighting DetailsI took photos from INSIDE a cruise ship, and I am so incredibly unimaginably STUPID that when I saw REFLECTIONS of lights from inside on the glass appear in my photos 'I could not believe my eyes. ' I do not know how I am capable of feeding or bathing myself. That is how stupid I am.
